<div class="main-hero user-home">
	<div class="main-hero-content">
		<h1>Welcome {{username}}</h1>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="main-content user-account-main">
	<div class="profile-options">
		<div class="hover-options edit-profile">
			<div>
				<h1>Edit Profile</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="line"></div>
			<p>Update your user profile and help us keep in contact by making
			sure your email address is current. Thanks again for choosing Events Fecth!</p>
		</div>
		<div class="hover-options search-events">
			<div>
				<h1>Search Events</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="line"></div>
			<p>Browse by category, date and location to find the most happening
			events around town. Even find out how many people are attending,
			average age and gender breakdown.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="hover-options tag-events">
			<div>
				<h1>Tag Events</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="line"></div>
			<p>Already know the event you will be attending. Tag it to help others
			find all the best events happening on any given day.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="user-form user-edit hidden">
		<h1>Edit Profile</h1><br>
		<form action="" class="cf">
			<div class="user-form-column1">
				<div class="field">
					<div class="label">
						<label>Username:</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input">
						<input type="text" name="uname" value="{{username}}">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="field">
					<div class="label">
						<label>Password:</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input">
						<input type="password" name="password" value="{{password}}">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="field">
					<div class="label">
						<label>Email:</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input">
						<input type="email" name="email" value="{{email}}">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="user-form-column2">						
				<div class="field">
					<div class="label">
						<label>Gender:</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input">
						<select name="gender" value="{{gender}}">
							<option value="male">Male</option>
							<option value="female">Female</option>
						</select>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="field">
					<div class="label">
						<label>Birth Year:</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input">
						<input type="text" name="birthyear" size="6" maxlength="4" value="{{birthyear}}">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="field">
					<div class="label">
						<label>Zip Code:</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input">
						<input type="text" name="zipCode" value="{{zip}}" size="6" maxlength="5">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="form-submit">
				<button class="submit-button">Submit</button>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	<div class="user-form user-tag hidden">	
		<h1>Tag Events</h1><br>	
		<form action="">
			<div class="field">
				<div class="label tool-label">
					<label>Event Name:</label>
				</div>
				<div class="input tool-input">
					<input type="search" name="name">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="field">
				<div class="label tool-label">
					<label>Event Date:</label>
				</div>
				<div class="input tool-input">
					<input type="date" >
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="form-submit">
				<button class="submit-button">Submit</button>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="secondary-content">
	<div class="user-results-divider">
		<h1 class="user-results-headline hidden">Event Matches</h1>
		<h1 class="todays-top-events">Top Events for {{today}}</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="media-event-bio-list">
		
	</div>
</div>